{"tid":1443504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣方向］中共行福建幫呢步棋根本錯晒","createTime":"2019-08-11T08:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:33:57.000Z","uid":302917,"like":694,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"916bc6dce706b20bf92b7554abbda291607189ef","tid":1443504,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:50:46.000Z","msg":"今日陳茂波仲出嚟譴責暴力，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府冇資格啊</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n前幾日中聯辦講嘅嘢，根本就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">煽動人民用暴力解決問題</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n藍絲連示威者都覺得係收錢搞事，何況係班福建佬呢？<br />\n唔通係佢地自己出錢買高鐵飛買機票住酒店？定同鄉會咁偉大自己bum水請同鄕嚟「保衛家園」啊？<br />\n<br />\n幕後金主係邊個？明眼人都知啦，所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣要煲大呢件事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n既然政府都鼓勵「市民」用暴力解決問題，仲有資格譴責示威者咩？<br />\n<br />\n所以文宣方向，要強調係政府唔肯回應訴求，反而喺香港鼓吹暴力。等佢地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以再用「譴責暴力」嚟反對示威活動</span></span>"},{"pid":"b1232f93d44787123d88ac6f70ccb8beab37d984","tid":1443504,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:50:58.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ace5a226129c5f2705d42b8fc843d59501a13112","tid":1443504,"uid":255336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be564acf0c94416f032a37f62cd5287e8b01a305","tid":1443504,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:51:09.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"30fd0a3264623c73004b0feaa03e8456f2950f69","tid":1443504,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"adca16f7628826f2149d4361d144c3cbb686e6d3","tid":1443504,"uid":276175,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:51:45.000Z","msg":"年輕人不嬲都唔暴力，更唔係暴徒！"},{"pid":"750ce5869e5ded9c260136987fc93931559f6ea2","tid":1443504,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply