d29e39","tid":1443504,"uid":111982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"916bc6dce706b20bf92b7554abbda291607189ef","tid":1443504,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:50:46.000Z","msg":"今日陳茂波仲出嚟譴責暴力，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府冇資格啊</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n前幾日中聯辦講嘅嘢，根本就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">煽動人民用暴力解決問題</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n藍絲連示威者都覺得係收錢搞事，何況係班福建佬呢？<br />\n唔通係佢地自己出錢買高鐵飛買機票住酒店？定同鄉會咁偉大自己bum水請同鄕嚟「保衛家園」啊？<br />\n<br />\n幕後金主係邊個？明眼人都知啦，所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣要煲大呢件事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n既然政府都鼓勵「市民」用暴力解決問題，仲有資格譴責示威者咩？<br />\n<br />\n所以文宣方向，要強調係政府唔肯回應訴求，反而喺香港鼓吹暴力。等佢地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以再用「譴責暴力」嚟反對示威活動</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:50:21.000Z","msg":"721都要追究埋"},{"pid":"93325e1ab8a9ebcb8d540fb7ea35bae5697b5db3","tid":1443504,"uid":88773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:51:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"11257544c441c6dae6819ce700ee64eb4200cda9","tid":1443504,"uid":40666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手整左張廢老系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017511eb93b864e1cc72d36647588fe478810040","tid":1443504,"uid":151304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"355244844b85695305796df0774a88befc8abb43","tid":1443504,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f6c1fcd18d947c0e9d2a663d2f48b16448c539","tid":1443504,"uid":100760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"721元朗恐襲政府警黑勾結"},{"pid":"80778ab1de422f479ea6b15a0f6d4c407347d954","tid":1443504,"uid":269965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99015c2c5a5a2efe2c683ffa66c1ddfc7e8e01c2","tid":1443504,"uid":51960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:59:27.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"588f34b1bb5a9a8ec79852400a386630beb8bd95","tid":1443504,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"ffa055b07a0184cbf8391ed790a274f9e0ab64cb","tid":1443504,"uid":226819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59ab434835efef049fbadb8b33aa68ff4da18770","tid":1443504,"uid":301820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"樓主天真過天真嬌<br />\n<br />\n共匪最強既招數係扭曲歷史.<br />\n大陸人根本唔知香港發生咩事.<br />\n外國人都係一知半解, 有些老鬼連香港係咩都唔知.<br />\n<br />\n當年64, 你睇下現在大陸文宣, 那些[精心修改剪輯]片段, <br />\n講到全部都是學生的錯, 學生使用暴力是不對, 領導都是人渣和收錢.<br />\n<br />\n我地4~5年既佔中, 已經不斷被共匪抹黑, <br />\n你去百度打佔中, 頂置就是 &lt;佔中&rdquo;是一场暴力骗局&gt;<br />\n<br />\n你以為大話講一百次係唔會變成真話<br />\n那麼共匪就將大話講夠一百<span style=\"color: red;\">[年]</span>肯定變成真話<br />\n(因為沒活人記得事實了)<br />\n<br />\n今天721只不過你們歷歷在目, <br />\n十年後他們就能將 727和721 的時間線調轉.<br />\n十五年後他們就把[精心修改剪輯]的片段放上網路和書上.<br />\n<br />\n今天福建幫, 元朗鄉黑, 都變成香港城管, 維持當年的治安.<br />\n香港人民和警察團結打狗, 狗是你們收了錢的外國勢力.<br />\n<br />\n所以香港今次輸左就玩撚完, 自己湊錢移民~"},{"pid":"38f0262e0f3e66c188567b8c4f3f1495a0e10b4d","tid":1443504,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:01:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"92ec2bd5d0ddc5d7bf551031e121d0e8a729ca32","tid":1443504,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:01:49.000Z","msg":"其實中共行福建幫呢步棋係玩火自焚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427678</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc8b2ca912453dcc27d89d6fea7d68610e37d93f","tid":1443504,"