src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53efa899473832e23572c1aaf9df0fc68ea933cf","tid":1443504,"uid":164690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a5e54da612a3c12090302d0f0eaf9fbf68d0405","tid":1443504,"uid":237739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"916bc6dce706b20bf92b7554abbda291607189ef","tid":1443504,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:50:46.000Z","msg":"今日陳茂波仲出嚟譴責暴力，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府冇資格啊</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n前幾日中聯辦講嘅嘢，根本就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">煽動人民用暴力解決問題</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n藍絲連示威者都覺得係收錢搞事，何況係班福建佬呢？<br />\n唔通係佢地自己出錢買高鐵飛買機票住酒店？定同鄉會咁偉大自己bum水請同鄕嚟「保衛家園」啊？<br />\n<br />\n幕後金主係邊個？明眼人都知啦，所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣要煲大呢件事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n既然政府都鼓勵「市民」用暴力解決問題，仲有資格譴責示威者咩？<br />\n<br />\n所以文宣方向，要強調係政府唔肯回應訴求，反而喺香港鼓吹暴力。等佢地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以再用「譴責暴力」嚟反對示威活動</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65df7583dcc10a9ae222d018c63c44a9542fd5f6","tid":1443504,"uid":84697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83b052e49027895c3732e8a0d963189a8f5128f0","tid":1443504,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b796471e974c9c088e58683bdef0565018e4edc4","tid":1443504,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"860eb59c35cd29fd60a45e7a08862309ff29e3c6","tid":1443504,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"佢地會話福建幫落黎打港獨<br />\n而微博上面班on9護旗手會拍手叫好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:51:35.000Z","msg":"所以唔可以俾佢地打到人，震憤佢地士氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:5